 Tflop，但console optimisation 隨時perform得好過 張有9 Tflop的GTX 1080"},{"pid":"037837fe4f487db9a8698056e3219a6046dc7682","tid":338176,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:36:28.000Z","msg":"明知自己冇時間玩都會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1508ea8d0904d1d2fea866c5dffd0d166bea852a","tid":338176,"uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:20:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實咁買法好病態<br />\n<br />\n17年我好似只爆過兩隻game</blockquote><br />\n唔病態<br />\n你知唔知console 界生存到依家都係因為有你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd4c4804931a9f06de33fae6069806552aae068","tid":338176,"uid":77771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:28:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實咁買法好病態<br />\n<br />\n17年我好似只爆過兩隻game</blockquote><br />\n唔病態<br />\n你知唔知console 界生存到依家都係因為有你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nconsole好在你買完保證玩到，唔駛set呢set路<br />\n<br />\n雖則近年又要dl patch又要install 又要update os <br />\n<br />\n已經無咗以前放隻碟入去就玩得的方便<br />\n<br />\n但總好過喺電度玩唔到forza 6都完全搵唔到原因同support<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nconsole,pc 真係各有各好的"},{"pid":"e42f3afd5dc1c01761f4345ec50207bcd45a1d3e","tid":338176,"uid":92936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:31:52.000Z","msg":"十幾年前我都覺得成堆機好變態 , 點知原來單一部機果d 仲變態 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全盛時期 : ps 1 / 2 , ss dc , n64 超任 擺左響一個幾層架度 , 鍾意玩邊部就玩邊部 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家就 ps4 switch 3ds psv , 不過老實講都真係越黎越無時間玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d20ac5b3c4fb6118edd45bcbdc1d6229aa86c3c","tid":338176,"uid":21279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:37:29.000Z","msg":"master race多數係唔打機是常識吧"},{"pid":"a707751d4decc1c3f9835b3d8c80316adf7e67f3","tid":338176,"uid":